      "description": "Straightforward, affordable, and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid project at an accessible price. It shows its age and wear, but offers real value for someone who appreciates a budget-conscious purchase from a trusted seller. Priced to move and presented with complete transparency.",
