    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget project or daily-with-attitude for the right buyer. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it still delivers a strong mechanical feel, a willing powertrain, and the kind of road manners that make it worth saving. Starts, runs, and drives, with the sort of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a well-used chassis. Great candidate for someone who appreciates straightforward hardware and doesn\u2019t mind putting in a little work to bring it to the next level. If you want an affordable entry point with real potential, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 5900.0,
