    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with a story to tell. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom perfect\u2014instead, it offers honest, well-traveled character and the kind of opportunity that savvy buyers love. Whether you\u2019re looking for an inexpensive runabout, a hands-on project, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with real presence, this one has the bones and personality to be something special. A practical choice for someone who sees potential instead of polish.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
