      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an affordable way into a set of wheels and could make a great budget runabout, first project, or handy spare car. If you\u2019re after something cheap and cheerful with potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
