      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Tough, usable driver with plenty of life left in the fundamentals. This one shows its age cosmetically, but it still delivers the kind of solid road feel and mechanical character enthusiasts appreciate. Engine pulls willingly, transmission does its job, and the chassis remains composed enough to make it a great budget commuter, shop truck, or starter project. A practical buy for someone who values drivetrain utility over showroom cosmetics, with the right bones to keep working and improve over time.",
